    "en": {
      "title": "A position in the ruling party for Kuttiarachi",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Deputy Organizers and Assistant Organizers of the ruling party in the Parliament were presented with appointment letters by Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena yesterday (27) at the Prime Minister's Office in Parliament.",
        "Accordingly, MPs Sagara Kariyawasam and Jayantha Katagoda were appointed as Deputy Organizers and MPs Kokila Gunawardena, Madhura Vithanage, and Tissa Kuttiarachchi as Assistant Organizers, received the relevant appointment letters from Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena.",
        "Minister Susil Premajayantha, Leader of the Parliament, Minister Prasanna Ranatunga, the Chief Organizer of the ruling party, as well as Mr. Chaminda Kularatne, Additional Secretary to the President and Secretary to the Chief Organizer of the Government Party, Harsha Wijewardene, Additional Secretary to the Prime Minister and Secretary to the Leader of the House joined the occasion."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Kuttiarachi",
          "label": "GPE"
